Package camzup.kotlin

Class KtComplex

java.lang.Object
camzup.core.Complex
camzup.kotlin.KtComplex
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Complex>
public class KtComplex
extends Complex
Provides Kotlin operator overloading support for complex numbers.
